{"build_type":"library","description":"Common worker runner (the single FS point for de-globalization). Context is the region; FIRST sets this thread's FS base to its own arena block (region[6], provisioned by the spawner) via arch_prctl, so every worker allocates from its OWN per-thread arena once the arena globals are FS-relative. Then p_addr=region[4], input=region[5]; invoke_computed_address(p_addr,[input])->result; deliver-worker-result-waking-doorbell-terminating-thread(region,result). Pre-flip the FS set is harmless (arena globals still shared); region[6]=0 from un-updated spawners -> SET_FS(0), also harmless until the flip.","module_name":"invoke-worker-at-address-delivering-result-terminating-thread","package_name":"invoke-worker-at-address-delivering-result-terminating-thread","function_definitions":{"invoke-worker-at-address-delivering-result-terminating-thread":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"context","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"four","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":4},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"five","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":5},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"p_addr","base":"context","index":"four","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"input","base":"context","index":"five","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"invoke_computed_address","address":"p_addr","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"input"}],"result_assignment_variable":"result"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"deliver-worker-result-waking-doorbell-terminating-thread","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"context"},{"kind":"var","value":"result"}],"result_assignment_variable":"r","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"result"}}]}}}